     FAAIPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        7  140SDATE
     I                                        1   60STIME
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PWAIT   1
      *
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C                     MOVEL'0'       PWAIT
      *
     C           0111      CHAINAAIPL111             44
     C           *IN44     IFEQ '0'
     C           CDTOHZ    IFGT SDATE
     C                     MOVEL'1'       PWAIT
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
